<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2011/08/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>open-video-downloader</id>
    <version>3.2.1</version>
    <title>Open Video Downloader</title>
    <authors>Jelle Glebbeek (and contributors)</authors>
    <owners>Adri</owners>
    <licenseUrl>https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/blob/master/LICENSE</licenseUrl>
    <projectUrl>https://jely2002.github.io/youtube-dl-gui/</projectUrl>
    <iconUrl>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui@master/renderer/img/icon.png</iconUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>A cross-platform GUI for youtube-dl made in Electron and node.js

### Features:

- Download from all kind of platforms: YouTube, vimeo, twitter and many more
- Download multiple videos/playlists/channels in one go
- Select the resolution and format you want to download in
- Download private videos (currently only tested on YouTube)
- Multithreaded, up to 32 videos can be downloaded synchronously
- Shows how much size the download will use up on your system
- The app automatically keeps ytdl up-to-date</description>
    <summary>A cross-platform GUI for youtube-dl made in Electron and node.js</summary>
    <releaseNotes>### Changelog

#### New &amp; improved features:
- Add input filters: (#[113](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/113), #[291](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/291))
    - Filter by date, size or custom yt-dlp match filters.
    - Select specific playlist items, including ranges.
- Add new ways to add to the queue: (#[505](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/505), #[322](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/322))
    - Import URLs from .txt or .csv files.
    - Paste multiple URLs in the input box.
    - Watch the clipboard to automatically add copied links.
- Improve output and post-processing settings. (#[691](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/691), #[708](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/708), #[753](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/753))
    - Re-encode videos to 30 fps.
    - Set the mp4 brand to mp42.
    - Save thumbnails as separate files. @wjx9
- Pass arbitrary yt-dlp extractor arguments. (#[709](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/709))
- Improve subtitle settings and selection. (#[766](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/766), #[779](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/779))
    - Separate creator-provided and auto-generated subtitles.
    - Choose subtitle formats and embedding per video.
- Split the settings page into multiple tabs.
- Improve codec selection to better match the selected quality. (#[756](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/756))
- Add a precise cut mode for partial downloads and SponsorBlock cuts. (#[763](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/763), #[765](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/765))
- Add an option to reverse playlist numbering. (#[783](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/783))

#### Bug fixes:
- Fix downloads failing when "Download all available subtitles" is enabled. (#[754](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/754))
- Fix some 4K videos not downloading correctly. (#[749](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/749))
- Use an empty string instead of None when metadata is missing in filename templates. (#[780](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/780))
- Fix the URL input not clearing after adding a link.
- Prevent HTML injection (mitigated by CSP) in clickable links and prevent sensitive yt-dlp arguments from being logged. (#[795](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/795)) @independent-arg

#### Languages:
- Add the Portuguese (Portugal) language. (#[729](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/729)) @BlackSpirits
- Improve the Spanish language. (#[801](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/801), #[808](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/808)) @independent-arg
- Update the Italian language. (#[725](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/725), #[733](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/733), #[767](https://github.com/jely2002/youtube-dl-gui/issues/767)) @bovirus</releaseNotes>
